# Keep the build context minimal and hermetic: only the llama.cpp source and
# the staging script are needed. Exclude host build artifacts (which carry
# absolute host paths in CMake caches), the staging dir, tarballs, and VCS
# metadata.
*
!llama.cpp
!scripts/stage-libs.sh
llama.cpp/_build
llama.cpp/build
**/.git
pkg
*.tar.gz
*.zip
